\ The logic x GC x continuations seam, one process, no image: force collections
\ while a logic-var binding and a captured continuation are live.

: shifter shift ;
: ex  reset 100 shifter 1 + ;        \ k adds 1 to its input
variable K   ex to K drop

\ a logic var bound to a heap structure survives an explicit collection
Y [( 1 2 3 null )] ~ drop
gc
Y ? . cr                             \ [( 1 2 3 null )]  binding + pair survived GC

\ a backtracking search that forces a GC at every step, with the captured
\ continuation held live throughout; commit to the first option over 4
[( 1 2 3 4 5 null )] [: |> opt | gc opt 4 gt if opt else fail then :] choose . cr   \ 5
50 K resume . cr                     \ 51  held continuation survived the search
bye
